'''贾斯万特·辛格·贾索尔'''（{{lang-en|Jaswant Singh Jasol}}，{{Pronunciation|En-us-Jaswant Singh from India pronunciation (Voice of America).ogg|pronunciation|help=no}}，{{bd|1938年|1月3日|2020年|9月27日|catIdx=Jasol}}），印度[[政治人物|政治人物]]，[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]创始成员<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rediff.com/news/special/jaswants-expulsion-is-the-bjps-gift-to-the-rss/20090820.htm|title=Jaswant's expulsion is the BJP's gift to the RSS|work=Rediff|access-date=2018-01-05|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225080511/https://www.rediff.com/news/special/jaswants-expulsion-is-the-bjps-gift-to-the-rss/20090820.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾任印度财政部长、外交部长、国防部长等职。

曾代表[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]五次（1980年、1986年、1998年、1999年、2004年）当选[[联邦院_(印度)|联邦院]]议员，四次（1990年、1991年、1996年、2009年）当选[[人民院_(印度)|人民院]]议员。

==生平==
1938年1月3日生于[[巴爾梅爾縣|巴爾梅爾縣]]贾索尔的一个[[拉傑普特人|拉傑普特人]]家庭<ref>{{cite news |title=In Rajasthan, Jaswant Singh's Son Banks On Rajput Anger, Father's Legacy |url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/in-rajasthan-jaswant-singhs-son-banks-on-rajput-anger-fathers-legacy-1954657 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |work=NDTV |date=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811230101/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/in-rajasthan-jaswant-singhs-son-banks-on-rajput-anger-fathers-legacy-1954657 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1957年至1966年在[[印度陆军|印度陆军]]服役，曾就读于[[梅奥学院|梅奥学院]]和[[印度国防学院|印度国防学院]]。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Quint|first=The|date=27 September 2020|title=RIP Jaswant Singh: Ex-Army Officer, Outstanding Parliamentarian|url=https://www.thequint.com/news/india/former-union-minister-jaswant-singh-passed-away-foreign-defense-finance-minister|access-date=27 September 2020|website=TheQuint|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082338/https://www.thequint.com/news/india/former-union-minister-jaswant-singh-passed-away-foreign-defense-finance-minister|11=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[1960年代|1960年代]]末开始从政。1980年代表[[印度人民党|印度人民党]]当选[[联邦院_(印度)|联邦院]]议员<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Dates That Defined the Life and Times of Jaswant Singh (1938-2020)|url=https://thewire.in/politics/jaswant-singh-passes-away-timeline-chronology-minister|access-date=2020-09-27|website=The Wire|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082336/https://thewire.in/politics/jaswant-singh-passes-away-timeline-chronology-minister|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1996年人民党击败国大党开始执政时，他在[[阿塔尔·比哈里·瓦杰帕伊|阿塔尔·比哈里·瓦杰帕伊]]内阁出任财政部长。但由于在国会未能取得多数支持，内阁仅十五天便倒台。两年后瓦杰帕伊再次就任印总理后，他出任[[外交部长|外交部长]]，2002年转任财政部长，直到2004年人民党在大选中落败<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-09-27|title=Jaswant Singh's illustrious political legacy— A snapshot|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/national/national-politics/jaswant-singhs-illustrious-political-legacy-a-snapshot-893642.html|access-date=2020-09-27|website=Deccan Herald|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082343/https://www.deccanherald.com/national/national-politics/jaswant-singhs-illustrious-political-legacy-a-snapshot-893642.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2001年，他被授予杰出议员奖<ref>{{Cite web|last=Quint|first=The|date=2020-09-27|title=RIP Jaswant Singh: Ex-Army Officer, Outstanding Parliamentarian|url=https://www.thequint.com/news/india/former-union-minister-jaswant-singh-passed-away-foreign-defense-finance-minister|access-date=2020-09-27|website=TheQuint|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082338/https://www.thequint.com/news/india/former-union-minister-jaswant-singh-passed-away-foreign-defense-finance-minister|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年至2009年，他担任[[联邦院_(印度)|联邦院]]反对党领袖<ref>{{Cite web|last=Varma|first=Gyan|date=2020-09-27|title=Jaswant Singh, key BJP face during Vajpayee era, passes away|url=https://www.livemint.com/news/india/jaswant-singh-key-bjp-face-during-vajpayee-era-passes-away-11601181994713.html|access-date=2020-09-27|website=mint|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082400/https://www.livemint.com/news/india/jaswant-singh-key-bjp-face-during-vajpayee-era-passes-away-11601181994713.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
2012年，他被[[全国民主联盟_(印度)|全国民主联盟]]提名为印度副总统人选<ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.thehindu.com/news/states/tamil-nadu/article3734513.ece| title= Jayalalithaa extends support to Jaswant Singh| date= 2012-08-06| accessdate= 2020-09-27| archive-date= 2018-12-25| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181225080516/https://www.thehindu.com/news/states/tamil-nadu/article3734513.ece| dead-url= no}}</ref>，但最终输给了[[穆罕默德·哈米德·安萨里|穆罕默德·哈米德·安萨里]]<ref>{{cite news| url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-16/india/32697388_1_nda-meeting-nda-candidate-hamid-ansari| title=Jaswant Singh to challenge Hamid Ansari test Vice-President's post| date=2012-07-16| accessdate=2020-09-27| archive-date=2013-12-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224123953/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-16/india/32697388_1_nda-meeting-nda-candidate-hamid-ansari| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

