2014年8月，他在家中的浴室不慎摔倒，头部严重受伤。2020年6月，他旧病复发，入住德里陆军医院，9月27日逝世，终年82岁<ref name="NDTV">{{cite web |last1=Sharma |first1=Akhilesh |title=Ex-Union Minister Jaswant Singh Dies At 82. "Saddened By Demise," Says PM |url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/former-union-minister-and-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dies-at-82-saddened-by-his-demise-tweets-pm-modi-2301608 |website=NDTV |accessdate=2020-09-27 |date=2019-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082335/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/former-union-minister-and-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dies-at-82-saddened-by-his-demise-tweets-pm-modi-2301608 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="TimesofIndia920">{{cite web |title=Former BJP leader Jaswant Singh passes away |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/former-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dead/articleshow/78343032.cms |website=The Times of India |accessdate=2020-09-27 |date=2020-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082419/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/former-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dead/articleshow/78343032.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ex-Union Minister Jaswant Singh Dies At 82. "Saddened By Demise," Says PM |url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/former-union-minister-and-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dies-at-82-saddened-by-his-demise-tweets-pm-modi-2301608 |accessdate=2020-09-27 |agency=NDTV |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082335/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/former-union-minister-and-bjp-leader-jaswant-singh-dies-at-82-saddened-by-his-demise-tweets-pm-modi-2301608 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==政策==
1999年，他率领代表团访华，双方确认中印关系发展的前提是互不视对方为威胁，[[中國－印度關係|中印关系]]由此步入改善和发展的进程<ref>{{cite web |author1=褚国飞 |title=中印大事记 |url=http://joul.cssn.cn/ddzg/ddzg_ldjs/wj/201010/t20101027_804925.shtml |publisher=[[中国社会科学报|中国社会科学报]] |date=2010-10-19 |accessdate=2020-09-27 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930150101/http://joul.cssn.cn/ddzg/ddzg_ldjs/wj/201010/t20101027_804925.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年，他公开表示，美印民用核能合作协议是一个“强加于人的”、“让印度羞辱的”协议，并要求执政的[[印度国大党|国大党]]联合政府重新就法案内容与美国进行协商<ref>{{cite web |title=核议题搅乱印度政坛 印美核能合作谈判仍未完成 |url=http://news.cctv.com/world/20061214/100328.shtml |publisher=CCTV |date=2006-12-14}}</ref>。

